Text: REPST I could tell you but then Id have to kill you Original Message From mailto Sent Wednesday December PM To HowardMJMAWBFTusmcmil Subject RE sweet yah jimi told me about the party and i will definitely be there im not happy about you deploying though dude do you know what your role will be definitely catch up when im back Original Message From Howard Capt Michael J HowardMJMAWBFTusmcmilENRON Sent Wednesday December PM To Richey Cooper Subject RE What up man Things have been extremely busy during the past days or so We are preparing to deploy on Jan I will be home with Tina from the th to the th I guess Jimi is having an engagement party on the st I would love it if you could make it to that You will need to talk to Jim for details Yes I am engaged Crazy huh It feels good though Tina and I are happy More to follow whence I see ya I have to run but just wanted to let you know I was hanging in there and doing well Peace Howie Original Message From Richey Cooper mailtoCooper NRONcom Sent Wednesday December PM To HowardMJMAWBFTusmcmil Subject hey dude i hear youre engaged congratulations whats going on i havent been in touch with anyone in the last year or so things have been going well in canada but my company is melting down so not sure what im going to be doing and probably wont know for awhile im going to be home dec jan are you going
